---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About the photographer behind FilmGallery">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none font-light leading-relaxed text-canvas-dark/80 space-y-6">
      <p>
        Welcome to FilmGallery — a personal archive of analog photography,
        curated one roll at a time.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every photograph here was captured on film, developed, and scanned —
        a deliberate process that values patience over speed, texture over
        perfection. Each roll tells its own story: the camera, the stock, the
        chemistry, and most importantly, the moments in between.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is as much a journal as it is a gallery. You'll find
        technical notes alongside each roll — the gear, the settings, the
        lab — and occasionally the stories behind the frames.
      </p>
      <p class="text-canvas-dark/50 italic">
        Thank you for stopping by. Feel free to leave a comment on any roll
        that resonates with you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
